> **Note:** Renderer-specific attributes depend on each renderer’s USD implementation.

---

## Installation

Clone or download the repository:

```
git clone https://github.com/yourname/pc-light-instancer.git
```

Copy the tool files into your Houdini user preferences directory:

```
$HOUDINI_USER_PREF_DIR
```

Restart Houdini, open Solaris, and launch the tool from the provided shelf or panel.

---

## Requirements

* Houdini 19.5+
* Solaris / USD workflows
* Point cloud–driven layouts
* Karma or Arnold for Solaris
* Tested on Windows and Linux

---

## Limitations

* Per-instance overrides are constrained by USD instancing rules
* Some advanced light parameters are renderer-specific
* Animated per-instance variations are limited by USD capabilities

